dataset: Bangladesh uptake analysis

washb_bangladesh_uptake.Rd

Bangladesh uptake analysis dataset

data(washb_bangladesh_uptake)

Format

A data frame with 14,908 observations and 18 variables.

dataid

Compound ID

clusterid

Cluster ID)

block

Randomization block ID

tr

Treatment assignment

svy

Survey round (0,1,2)

svydate

Survey date

storewat

Store drinking water (q10001)

freechl

Free chlorine detected in stored water (>0 mg/L)

latseal

Latrine has functional water seal (q809_9a)

latfeces

No visible feces on slab/floor of latrine

humfeces

No human feces observed in house/compound (q4201,4203,4205)

hwsw

Prim handwashing loc has water (q704_1)

hwss

Prim handwashing loc has soap (q704_2-6)

hwsws

Prim handwashing loc has water+soap (q704_1-6)

lnsn

LNS sachets consumed per week

lnsp

Percent of expected LNS sachets consumed

rlnsn

LNS sachets consumed per week (reported)

rlnsp

Percent of expected LNS sachets consumed (reported)
